      "label": "Zero Build Step Design",
      "file_type": "rationale",
      "source_file": "README.md",
      "source_location": null,
      "source_url": null,
      "captured_at": null,
      "author": null,
      "contributor": null,
      "rationale": "Runs directly in the browser with native ES module imports — no bundler, no transpiler, no build pipeline. Reduces complexity and deployment friction."
    },
    {
      "id": "rationale_anti_detection",
      "label": "Anti-Detection Design Rationale",
      "file_type": "rationale",
      "source_file": "AGENTS.md",
      "source_location": null,
      "source_url": null,
      "captured_at": null,
      "author": null,
      "contributor": null,
      "rationale": "Playwright is patched at node_modules level to automatically apply stealth plugins (playwright-ghost + patchright) so any code importing playwright gets anti-detection by default. Purpose: pass bot detection on fingerprint-heavy sites like WhatsApp Web."
    },
